node.text:
I feel so emotional writing this and wondering where did the time go? Although Camila can’t read this I want to just share with you all how blessed I feel to be her mommy. Becoming a mother has been one of the biggest gifts that life has given me, it not only changed the world around me but changed me to be the person I am today. 
...................................................................
A year ago today I was anticipating the moment of meeting you. Wondering who you would be like? Would you look like mommy? Would you look like daddy? Even tho you are the spitting image of your father down to your personality I grew you inside of me and loved you before even meeting you. You’re such a smart, funny and beautiful little girl. Thank you for changing my life and filling me with so much love & happiness. I love you. Happy Birthday. 🤍

node.text: I’ve always been very open about myself love journey. I’ve shared the lowest points in my life, but I’m so happy that I can share with you guys what makes me feel my best. When I look and smell good, I feel like the best version of me and I’m currently obsessed with @esteelauder #BeautifulMagnolia fragrance. Its floral essence makes me feel fresh and unstoppable. Just remember you are enough baby girl. 💕 #esteepartner

node.text: From the moment I met Ulysses, we had this connection I’ve never had before. He made me feel loved, cared for, and beautiful all at once. I’ve always said fragrance is such an important part of my life, because it reminds me of those moments.  Recently, I’ve been loving @esteelauder #BeautifulMagnolia fragrance. It’s a floral fragrance and a scent that gives off a romantic, fresh and radiant smell. Make sure to check it out on EsteeLauder.com if you’re looking for a new scent to try 💓  #esteepartner

node.text: Where do I even start, honestly no words could ever express my love and appreciation for you. Not just today but everyday we celebrate you.
